OL,5, Family members of the 2012 Sandy Hook  
OL,6, school shooting victims offered to     
OL,7, settle the $1.5bn (#1.32bn) debt owed  
OL,8, by conspiracy theorist Alex Jones.     
OL,10,FThey said they would accept the sale of
OL,11,FMr Jones's assets, or a minimum of $85m
OL,12,F(#67m) over 10 years.                  
OL,14,FMr Jones admitted making repeated false
OL,15,Fclaims about the deaths, which led to  
OL,16,Fharassment of the victims' families.   
OL,18,FThe Sandy Hook families sued Jones over
OL,19,Fthose false claims and won the $1.5bn  
OL,20,Fjudgement last year.                   
